```

### Key Points

- Use `data-invalid` on `Field` for error styling
- Use `aria-invalid` on form controls
- Use `htmlFor` on labels for accessibility
- `orientation="responsive"` switches layout at container width
- Works with all form controls (Input, Select, Checkbox, etc.)

